{
  "chapter": "080",
  "title": "乐毅列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "乐氏渊源",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>，他的先<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">祖</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span>之将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灵寿</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>死，葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灵寿</span>，其后<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>就家于此。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>后又复国，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵武灵王</span>时又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>，而<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">乐氏</span>后代中有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "委质于燕",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>贤能，好<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>事，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人举荐他。待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵武灵王\">武灵王（赵武灵王）</span>有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沙丘</span>之乱，便离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>之乱被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>怨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，未曾有<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一日（时长）</span>忘报<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之仇。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕国</span>小，辟远，无力制服，于是屈身下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，先礼待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郭隗</span>以招贤者。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>于是为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏昭王\">昭王（魏昭王）</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王以客<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>待他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>辞让，便委质称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>任他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亚卿</span>，过了很久。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "济西破齐",
      "text": "当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>强盛，南面在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">重丘</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐眛</span>，西面在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">摧</span>折<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三晋</span>，便与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三晋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，扩地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀里</span>。与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>争重而称帝，不久又废帝号。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都想背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>而归服<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>骄矜，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不能承受。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>问<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>是霸国的余业，地大<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人</span>众，不易独自<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>之。王若一定要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>之，不如联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。\" 于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>约<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵惠文王</span>，另派使者联络<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>用<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之利诱劝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>恼恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>骄暴，都争相<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>一起<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>回报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>尽起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵惠文王</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>授<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>便统率<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>之<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济西</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>罢归，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>独自<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span>击，直至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济西</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>后，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span>走，退保<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>独自留下扫平<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>城都闭门防守。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>，尽<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之珍宝财物<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">祭器</span>，运往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>大悦，亲到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济上</span>慰劳军队，犒赏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌国</span>，号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐毅\">昌国君（乐毅）</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>收<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的战利品而归，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>继续以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>平定尚未攻下的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>城。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "下齐七十余城",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地扫荡<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五岁（时长）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀城</span>，都作为郡县归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，只有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span>未归服。恰逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>死，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕惠王\">惠王（燕惠王）</span>做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>时就不喜欢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>，即位后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span>听说，便在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国散布反间计说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>城未<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>的只有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两城</span>。然而之所以不早<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>，是因为听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>新王有嫌隙，想继续拥兵留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，南面称王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>所担心的，只怕别的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将</span>来。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠王</span>本已怀疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>，得<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>反间计，便派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span>代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>为将，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>回国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠王</span>不友好地取代他，怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，便西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>，号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐毅\">望诸君（乐毅）</span>。尊宠<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>以警动<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "田单复齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span>后来与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，果然设诈<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诳</span>骗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军，便在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span>之下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span>，转<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>兵，北至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河上</span>，尽复得<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>城，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>迎<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐襄王\">襄王（齐襄王）</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "燕王遗书责",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠王</span>后悔派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span>代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>，因此<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>军<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span>将丢失<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地；又怨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，怕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>乘<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>之敝<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠王</span>便派人责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>，并表示歉意说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>以全国托付给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，报<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>之雠，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>没有不震动的，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>岂敢<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一日（时长）</span>忘<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>之功！恰逢<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>弃<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>而去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>新即位，左右误导<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span>代<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，是因<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>久暴露于外，所以召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>暂且休息，商议大事。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>误听传言，以与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>有隙，便弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>自作打算尚可，可又怎能回报<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>厚待<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>之意呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠王</span>一封<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>说："
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "不敢奉命",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不才，不能奉承王命，以顺左右之心，怕伤<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>之明，有害足下之义，所以逃<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">奔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。如今足下派人列数我的罪过，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>担心侍御之人不察<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>所以畜养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span>之道，又不能表明<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所以事<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>之心，所以敢以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>作答。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "先王知人",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说贤圣之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不以禄位偏爱亲近之人，功多者赏之，有能者任之。所以察能而授<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">官</span>，是成功之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>；论行而结交，是立名之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下观察<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的举动，见其有高出世主之心，所以假借<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符节</span>，得以在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>被察见。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>过奖，把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>置于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>之中，立于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>之上，不谋于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父兄</span>，任为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亚卿</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>自认为奉令承教，可幸无罪，所以受命不辞。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "伐齐大功",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>命令说：\"我对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>有积怨深怒，不考虑自己的力量薄弱，想以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>为事。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，是霸国的余业，是遗存最多胜迹的国家。娴熟于<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>，惯于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>。王若要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>它，必须与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共谋。与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共谋，不如结交<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。况且<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮北</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>地，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>想得的，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>若答应而约四国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>之，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>可大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>以为然，备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>南使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。回复命令后，发<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。凭天道和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>之灵，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河北</span>之地都随<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>而归，到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济上</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济上</span>之军受命<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人。轻卒锐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>，长驱入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>都。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王逃奔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>，仅以身免；珠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span>财<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>珍<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">器</span>尽入于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">器</span>具陈设于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宁台</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">大吕</span>钟陈列于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">元英</span>宫，故<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎</span>归于磨室，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓟丘</span>的树木植于汶水竹丛之地，自<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五伯</span>以来，功劳未有及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>者。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>以为称心如意，所以裂地封我，使我得以比诸小国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>自认为奉命承教，可幸无罪，所以受命不辞。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "贤君教后世",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说贤圣之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，功立而不废，所以载于<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>；先知之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，成名而不毁，所以称于后世。像<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>报怨雪耻，平服<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之强国，收其<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八百岁（时长）</span>之积累，到他弃<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>之日，遗教未衰，执<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>任事之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，修<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法令</span>，慎待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶孽</span>，施及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">萌隶</span>，都可以教导后世。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "伍子胥故事",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说，善作者未必善成，善始者未必善终。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>的话被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖闾</span>采纳，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王远行至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>不以为是，赐他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鸱夷</span>而浮于江。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王不觉悟先前的论断可以立功，所以把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">沈</span>入江中不悔；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>没早点看出两位君主的不同气量，所以到了入江也不变。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "免身立功",
      "text": "免身立功，以彰明<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的事迹，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的上策。遭受毁辱的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">诽谤</span>，堕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>之名，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>最畏惧的。面临不测之罪，以侥幸谋利，是道义所不敢为的。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "君子交绝",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说古代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>，交绝不出恶声；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">忠臣</span>离国，不洁身自白。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>虽不才，多次受教于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>。担心侍御之人亲近左右之说，不察疏远者的行为，所以敢献此<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>，望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>王留意。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "乐毅卒于赵",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王又以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">昌国君</span>；而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>来往再次通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>都以他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客卿</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "乐间谏伐赵",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>居<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十馀年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬喜\">王喜（姬喜）</span>采用他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>之计，想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，而问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">昌国君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>是四<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>之国，其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>熟习<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>事，不可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王不听，便<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>之，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄗</span>大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>之军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">禽</span>获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>的同宗。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">奔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>便<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>割重地与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>讲和，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>才撤围离去。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "燕王招乐间",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王恨不用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>之计，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>已在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，便遗<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>说：\"纣的时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>不被任用，冒死进谏不止，以希望他听从；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商容</span>不达，自身祇受屈辱，以希望他改变。等到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>心不向他，狱囚自行逃出，然后两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>退隐。所以纣背负桀暴之累，两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>不失忠圣之名。为什么？他们的忧患用尽了。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>虽然愚笨，但不像纣那样暴虐；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>虽乱，也不像<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>那样严重。室有语，不能尽言于里，就告诉邻里。这两种做法，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>不认为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>会取其一。\""
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "乐乘封武襄",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>怨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>不听其计，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐乘\">武襄君（乐乘）</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "秦灭赵",
      "text": "第二年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>以重<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>求和，才解围。此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五岁（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">孝成王（赵孝成王）</span>死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵悼襄王\">襄王（赵悼襄王）</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "高帝封乐叔",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十馀年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>路过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，问：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>有后代吗？\" 回答说：\"有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐叔</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">乐卿</span>，号<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐叔\">华成君（乐叔）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐叔\">华成君（乐叔）</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子。而<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">乐氏</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>中有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐瑕公</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐臣公</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>，他们<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">亡</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高密</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐臣公</span>善修<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">老子</span>之学说，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>显闻，被称为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤师</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：起初<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒯通</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主父偃</span>读<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕王</span>的回<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>，未尝不放下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>而泣的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐臣公</span>学<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">老子</span>之学，他的本师号<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">河上丈人</span>，不知其所出。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">河上丈人</span>教<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安期生</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安期生</span>教<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛翕公</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛翕公</span>教<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐瑕公</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐瑕公</span>教<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐臣公</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐臣公</span>教<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高密</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胶西</span>教学，做了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹相国</span>的老师。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "昌国忠谠，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>所无。 连<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>五国，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济西</span>为墟。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>王中反间，空闻报<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">义士</span>慷慨，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">明君</span>轼闾。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐间\">间（乐间）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐乘\">乘（乐乘）</span>继任为将，芳规不变。"
    }
  }
}